            <summary class="cursor-pointer list-none px-5 sm:px-6 py-4 sm:py-5 font-bold text-base sm:text-lg text-gray-900 flex items-center justify-between hover:bg-gradient-to-r hover:from-indigo-50 hover:to-purple-50 transition-all duration-200 rounded-2xl">
